Class ActiveRegion

java.lang.Object
  jeune_Trie.ActiveRegion
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class ActiveRegion
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable

This class will be used to tell the what region of the board is being actively manipulated. It defines the area of possible change.
